{"tid":1109714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(TVB) 無線宣佈 封殺壹傳媒/蘋果日報","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T11:13:53.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f88cc32133413b7f40ae6c83a8ed48ed29e8b9","tid":1109714,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"有讀者向《主場新聞》提供一份即將發出的無綫電視聲明，聲明宣布將壹傳媒列為「不受歡迎傳媒」的聲明。聲明又指，無綫將全面封殺壹傳媒所有刊物，未來任何無綫電視公司及藝員活動，將會不接受包括《蘋果日報》等壹傳媒記者採訪。 <br />\n<br />\n無綫宣傳科副總監曾醒明接受《主場》電話查詢，表示聽聞公司有如此安排，但未收到公司正式通知。他又指，若果有消息，稍後會作出正式公布。 <br />\n<br />\n無綫聲明全文： <br />\n<br />\n「壹傳媒集團屬下的刊物，就免費電視牌照事件長期針對無綫電視，作出失實報道，發牌與否為政府決定，絕非無綫電視可能影響，壹媒體在毫無理據下恣意攻擊和醜化，已遠超出新聞媒體應有的報道做法和行為，其目的昭然若揭，顯而易見。 <br />\n<br />\n最近趁着無綫電視台慶，壹傳媒的蘋果日報及動新聞變本加厲，展開狙擊和抹黑的行動，歇斯底里的謾罵，更呼籲全港熄機行動，煽動白色恐怖。 <br />\n<br />\n無綫電視有必要保衛公司商譽，決定即時開始，把壹傳媒屬下所有刊物，列為不受歡迎媒體，本公司及藝員活動不接受其記者採訪。」"},{"pid":"28fa58fb11ec25ba6018d225751fcb32c184d70d","tid":1109714,"uid":145247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d44c7c5149e6ee8837f264e2ca580f007967568","tid":1109714,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314ecf729f32bbf8d20f4484250d7aa55e5853e6","tid":1109714,"uid":224453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"TVB on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4833b7d0658139741bc3df5558b188259e8a1dd","tid":1109714,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"Old news?"},{"pid":"97114d0c0edd673ac7eb62a7d869ed93d1adf720","tid":1109714,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">表示聽聞公司有如此安排，但未收到公司正式通知。</span><br />\n<br />\n公司發言人點會咁答，呢D一定係答唔知 或者稍後會公布"},{"pid":"8622ced77415d6f69a94f8d125e490b68ee4b10c","tid":1109714,"uid":178579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:04:36.000Z","msg":"小氣了"},{"pid":"1de05dc39bc45e48147dff45e155cacae6d9298b","tid":1109714,"uid":40682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"曾醒明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過咗檔啦"},{"pid":"bbee9cdb53cd6c2c0dddd7ad82963048df7b7416","tid":1109714,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"失實？啱啱許志安出嚟講咗嘅又係唔係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf847e817c242b454d1bffd8a6bc7e7d0ca649b","tid":1109714,"uid":43328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"果然係Child登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84362b602d655a19ed86a42c738dcf0faea3796f","tid":1109714,"uid":31837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"呢段幾耐之前？"}]}